about:
Hi, I'm Raquel!

I'm an illustrator and biology nerd who likes to tell stories. I like to experiment with textures to give my digital work a more traditional feel, 

I gravitate toward drawing whimsical characters, cats, cephalopods, my dog, and fantasy creatures inspired by them.
